title: Guns of Navaron+Force 10 from Navarone 2xDvDs
description:
Spoofy,s Party Pack - Two Classic War Movies


So, Slouch on the Couch and Crack those Snacks


DVD 1 - The Guns of Navarone with Gregory Peck,  David Niven, Anthony Quinn (1961)

English Audio

English Subs

A British team is sent to cross occupied Greek territory and destroy the massive German gun emplacement that commands a key sea channel.



Dvd 2 - Force 10 from Navarone with Robert Shaw, Edward Fox, Harrison Ford (1978)

Audio English

Subs English / Danish / Finnish / Icelandic / Norwegian / Swedish

During World War II, several oddly assorted military experts are teamed in a mission to raid and destroy a bridge vital to enemy strategy.
